<title>
DTC C1141 / C1142 / C1143 / C1145
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B6304013001">
<title>
DTC Detecting Condition and Trouble Area
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "4.347in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.778in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
DTC detecting condition
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Trouble area
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
C1141: P/S Motor Circuit Voltage Malfunction
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Voltage between P/S motor terminals exceeds upper limit (8.5 V) or lower limit (0.2 V) for more than specified time.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
P/S control module
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
P/S motor (steering column assembly)
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
C1142: P/S Motor Circuit Current Malfunction 1
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measured P/S motor drive current is bigger than target value by 10 A or more.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
C1143: P/S Motor Circuit Current too Big
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measured P/S motor drive current is more than 50 A.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
C1145: P/S Motor Circuit Current Malfunction 2
</emph>
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Measured P/S motor drive current is less than 2 A continuously for more than 5 seconds even though target P/S motor drive current is more than 4 A.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Measured P/S motor drive current is less than 0.8 A and P/S motor control duty is more than 90% for total 1 second even though target P/S motor drive current is less than 8 A.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
